License:        GPL-1.0-or-later OR Artistic-1.0-Perl
URL:            http://www.template-toolkit.org/
Source0:        https://cpan.metacpan.org/authors/id/T/TO/TODDR/Template-Toolkit-%{version}.tar.gz
